library(data.table)

mydata = fread("F:\\大数据\\大数据统计基础可视化课程数据集\\1数据集一：Wind数据\\dailyprice.txt",sep = '\t',header = T)
#summary(mydata)
mydata$trade_code = as.factor(mydata$trade_code)
mydata$trade_status = as.factor(mydata$trade_status)

mydata1 = mydata[mydata$datetime == "2003-7-23",c("volume","amt","chg","turn","trade_status")]
mydata1 = mydata1[complete.cases(mydata1),]
library(ggplot2)
#直方图
ggplot(mydata1,aes( x = chg)) + geom_histogram(fill = "darkgreen")
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

#气泡图
ggplot(mydata1,aes( x = chg,y = amt, size = turn,color = trade_status)) + geom_point(alpha=0.25)

#散点矩阵图
library(car)
scatterplotMatrix(mydata1[,2:5],main = "Scatter plot Matrix")

#相关系数矩阵
library(corrplot)
cormatrix = cor(mydata1[,2:4],use = "complete.obs")
corrplot(cormatrix)

#密度图
ggplot(data = mydata1,aes(x = log(turn),y = chg))+geom_point()+stat_density2d(aes(colour = ..level..))
## Warning: Removed 5 rows containing non-finite values (stat_density2d).

#热度图
mydata1$turn1 = Hmisc::cut2(mydata1$turn,g=5)
mydata1$amt1 = Hmisc::cut2(mydata1$amt,g=5)
ggplot(mydata1,aes(x = turn1, y = amt1,fill = log(volume)))+geom_tile()

#平行坐标图
library(lattice)
mydata2 = mydata[1:20,c(2,7:16)]
parallel(~mydata2,mydata2,group=trade_code,horizontal.axis = FALSE)
## Warning: 'parallel' is deprecated.
## Use 'parallelplot' instead.
## See help("Deprecated")

#雷达图
stars(mydata2[1:9,2:7],locations=c(0,0),col.lines = 2:7,radius = FALSE,scale = TRUE,key.loc = c(0,0),lwd = 1.5)

#直方图叠加密度曲线
mydata3 = mydata[1:5000,c('open','close')]
mydata3 = na.omit(mydata3)
ggplot(mydata3,aes( x = open )) + geom_histogram(aes(y=..density..),fill = "darkgreen") +geom_line(aes(y = ..density..),stat = 'density')
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

#箱线图和小提琴图
mydata3$cate = c(rep(1,2000),rep(2,1985),rep(3,1000))
mydata3$cate = as.factor(mydata3$cate)
#箱线图
ggplot(mydata3, aes(x= cate,y=open,group = cate)) + 
  geom_boxplot(outlier.colour="red", outlier.shape=8, outlier.size=4)

#小提琴图
ggplot(mydata3,aes(x=cate,y=open,group = cate,color = cate))+geom_violin(alpha=0.8,width=1,aes(fill = cate))

# t-分布
set.seed(1)
x = seq(-5,5,length.out=100)
y = pt(x,1)
# t-分布累积分布函数图
plot(x,y,col="red",xlim=c(-5,5),ylim=c(0,1),type='l',ylab='density',xlab='',
     main="The Normal Cumulative Distribution")
lines(x,pt(x,2),col = "green")
lines(x,pt(x,3),col = "blue")
lines(x,pt(x,4),col = "grey")

# t-分布概率密度函数图
set.seed(1)
x = seq(-5,5,length.out=100)
y = dt(x,1)
plot(x,y,col="red",xlim=c(-5,5),ylim=c(0,0.5),type='l',
     xaxs="i", yaxs="i",ylab='density',xlab='',
     main="The Normal Density Distribution")
lines(x,dt(x,2),col = "green")
lines(x,dt(x,3),col = "blue")
lines(x,dt(x,4),col = "grey")

# 卡方分布
set.seed(1)
x = seq(0,100,length.out=100)
y = pchisq(x,20)
# 卡方分布累积分布函数图
plot(x,y,col="red",xlim=c(0,100),ylim=c(0,1),type='l',ylab='density',xlab='',
     main="The Normal Cumulative Distribution")
lines(x,pchisq(x,30),col = "green")
lines(x,pchisq(x,40),col = "blue")
lines(x,pchisq(x,50),col = "grey")

# 卡方分布概率密度函数图
set.seed(1)
x = seq(0,100,length.out=100)
y = dchisq(x,20)
plot(x,y,col="red",xlim=c(0,100),ylim=c(0,0.1),type='l',
     xaxs="i", yaxs="i",ylab='density',xlab='',
     main="The Normal Density Distribution")
lines(x,dchisq(x,30),col = "green")
lines(x,dchisq(x,40),col = "blue")
lines(x,dchisq(x,50),col = "grey")

x = seq(0,100,length.out=100)
cul20 = pchisq(x,20)
cul30 = pchisq(x,30)
cul40 = pchisq(x,40)
cul50 = pchisq(x,50)

den20 = dchisq(x,20)
den30 = dchisq(x,30)
den40 = dchisq(x,40)
den50 = dchisq(x,50)
x_new = rep(x,4)
cul_new = c(cul20,cul30,cul40,cul50)
den_new = c(den20,den30,den40,den50)
col = c(rep(20,100),rep(30,100),rep(40,100),rep(50,100))
data = data.frame(x_new,cul_new,den_new,col)

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data = data,aes(x =x_new,y = cul_new,col = col,group = col))+geom_line(col = col)+
  labs(x="x",y="",title = "卡方分布累积分布图")

ggplot(data = data,aes(x =x_new,y = den_new,col = col,group = col))+geom_line(col = col)+
  labs(x="x",y="",title = "卡方分布概率密度图")
